{"id":588661,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/中国数字时代-刘霞已抵达柏林（更新）/","date":"2018-07-10T18:06:03Z","modified":"2018-07-10T18:05:33Z","title":"中国数字时代 | 刘霞已抵达柏林（更新）","content":"<p>中国数字时代核实：刘霞已经于当地时间2018年7月10日中午抵达欧洲。前往赫尔辛基机场接机的朋友，为她拍摄了两张照片，发布于社交媒体。</p>\n<p>目前刘霞已经抵达柏林。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_588677\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-588677\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/Image-from-iOS-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"382\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/Image-from-iOS-1-300x208.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/Image-from-iOS-1-768x533.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/Image-from-iOS-1.jpg 798w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">刘霞到达柏林</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_588669\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-588669\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0122-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0122-1-300x199.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0122-1-768x509.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0122-1.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">刘霞已经抵达欧洲，图为她在赫尔辛基机场转机。</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_588663\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-588663\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0124-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"978\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0124-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0124-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/IMG_0124-576x1024.jpg